      "relevance": "115%"
    },
    {
      "layer": 1,
      "layer_name": "Domain Knowledge (This Company)",
      "header": "Mock Interview → Video Call UI (Feb 10 2026 — SHIPPED)",
      "content": "## Mock Interview → Video Call UI (Feb 10 2026 — SHIPPED)\n- **UI Redesign**: Dark video call layout replacing chat-bubble interface. AI avatar (center) pulses + animated waveform bars when speaking. Candidate camera in PiP (bottom-right)\n- **Controls**: Green mic button (record), camera toggle, transcript toggle, end-call button\n- **Question Display**: Subtle overlay on video (replaces chat context)\n- **Voice Always Active**: No toggle needed — video call experience by default\n- **Token Fix**: Voice functions were reading `localStorage.getItem('token')` (null) instead of `getToken()` helper → 401 on every TTS/voice-respond call. Fixed by using proper auth helper\n- **Status**: ✅ Shipped live, zero errors post-deploy",
